---
// Repeating bio/CTA section that appears at the bottom of every page
---

<section id="connect" class="bg-[var(--color-light-bg)] py-20 px-6" aria-labelledby="hello-section-heading">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h2 id="hello-section-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-charcoal)] mb-8 leading-tight">
        Hello!
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-[var(--color-dark-gray)] leading-relaxed mb-10">
        I'm Lisa Wilkins. I've spent 17+ years as a UX director, designer, and product strategist building things people actually want to use — across media, news, tech, and education at organizations like NBCUniversal, PragerU, and Microsoft. I live in the Sonoran Desert, which inspires me daily with its simplicity on the surface and complexity underneath. I'm adaptable, resilient, and nerdy — ask me about WCAG compliance or horse training and you'll get the same enthusiasm. I'm most proud of raising a son full of gratitude and spoiling a very good dog.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-charcoal)] mb-8">
        Let's talk about what I can build with your team.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@lisawilkins.com"
          class="inline-block bg-[var(--color-coral)] hover:bg-[var(--color-coral-hover)] text-white text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-8 py-4 rounded-md transition-colors"
        >
          hello@lisawilkins.com
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lisawilkins"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block border-2 border-[var(--color-charcoal)] hover:border-[var(--color-coral)] hover:text-[var(--color-coral)] text-[var(--color-charcoal)] text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-8 py-4 rounded-md transition-colors"
        >
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
